{"tid":1954543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本救世界】富士流感藥治中國病毒 開始最後臨床實驗階段","createTime":"2020-04-02T02:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T06:52:59.000Z","uid":54373,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4ba10b0ae8186c0a195ee0a7c32424d4714bd3","tid":1954543,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"富士旗下藥廠的治流感藥Avigan，通稱favipiravir，有望成為治療新冠肺炎藥物。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎在全球大爆發，各國與時間競賽研製治療藥物，日本富士公司(Fujifilm)旗下藥廠周二宣布，其流感藥Avigan已進入最後人類臨床實驗階段。該藥可阻止流感病毒在人體內自我複製，研究員相信它對新冠病毒有相同功效。Avigan通稱favipiravir，3月起在愛知縣的藤田醫科大學醫院等開始做臨床實驗 ，並成功通過首兩階段的臨床實驗，而最後階段實驗將在東京都的醫院進行，約100名新冠肺炎患者將參與，實驗會至6月底。另外，因Avigan對胎兒產生副作用，孕婦不能使用。"},{"pid":"abe3bfc1c4fbf9a9cbce4b573dec21d3afdadd32","tid":1954543,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69d48e1a0c770881712f17559fb71ea73b032640","tid":1954543,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb66a3bc4dc14bdcde07a046bf254854dea1d28","tid":1954543,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"5毛又唔敢留言？"},{"pid":"8ce5315a56725653c91898144edac4906c944c1d","tid":1954543,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d406d6be41c50052e94c04371a7eccb98a777a3e","tid":1954543,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"真係just a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10611c31e073707d422d51f20d1a4f45ac89a1b8","tid":1954543,"uid":71213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:07:49.000Z","msg":"In 富士 I trust<img src=\